public class LazyMBeanManagerAtomicReference<T>
extends java.util.concurrent.atomic.AtomicReference<T>

This is a helper class to lazy create a reference to an MBeanManager when the getLazyRef method is called.

Method Detail

getLazyRef

public T getLazyRef()
This is called to fetch the instance. It is created the first time this method is called. It's possible for two instances to be created but the JMX MBean Server will reject one when it is registered and throws an InstanceAlreadyExists exception in this case.

Returns:
